  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/cfda471bba30dc7002c3aad40f60603b.poster.avif?t=1760529911\" width=598 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/cfda471bba30dc7002c3aad40f60603b.webm?t=1760529911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/cfda471bba30dc7002c3aad40f60603b.mp4?t=1760529911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build and protect cities with factories in an infinite hex world.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Best way to play the game: Singleplayer / Mouse and Keyboard.</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Balance production and consumption of your city.<br></li><li> Research new technologies,<br></li><li> Build more factories, <br></li><li> Build more cities,<br></li><li> Explore new tiles and new planets,<br></li><li> Protect your cities from alien sabotage,<br></li><li> Use the Map Maker to build your own worlds, <br></li><li> Get Steam Achievements, <br></li><li> Compare with other players with the Steam Leaderboards!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer Online Stock Exchange.</h2>Reach tier 5 to be able to trade items in the Stock Market with other players online in real-time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/b2d4ed1c7f75b20d0c7a9e948a8fbcb6.poster.avif?t=1760529911\" width=598 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/b2d4ed1c7f75b20d0c7a9e948a8fbcb6.webm?t=1760529911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/b2d4ed1c7f75b20d0c7a9e948a8fbcb6.mp4?t=1760529911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features in this prototype:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 41 Initial Buildings (Build Roads, Miners, Farms, Factories, Houses and Services)<br></li><li> 15 Initial types of Tiles<br></li><li> 7 Research areas<br></li><li> 2 Citizen class<br></li><li> 1 Alien Saboteur class<br></li><li> 1 Spaceship class<br></li><li> 39 Parts to produce<br></li><li> 2 Planets (Earth and Moon)<br></li><li> Terraforming<br></li><li> Testing phase of the Online Stock Market</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/8db0c03d2a72fb4be4ab93ffdacd3a5a.poster.avif?t=1760529911\" width=598 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/8db0c03d2a72fb4be4ab93ffdacd3a5a.webm?t=1760529911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/8db0c03d2a72fb4be4ab93ffdacd3a5a.mp4?t=1760529911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Some <strong>thoughts </strong>for the next versions of the game: </h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> + new Buildings (More factories, farms, power generators, miners...)<br></li><li> + new tile types (Desert, uranium, pasture, bauxite, oil...)<br></li><li> + parts to produce ( Canned Food, Tools, Satellites, Smartphones...)<br></li><li> + Citizen Classes (Engineers, Scientists, Ecologists...)<br></li><li> + types of houses<br></li><li> + types of services (Health Center, School, Stadium...)<br></li><li> Manual Turrets, Automatic Turrets and Spaceship to fight new enemies</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/77571eb457a0001debf7f484b17297b5.poster.avif?t=1760529911\" width=598 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/77571eb457a0001debf7f484b17297b5.webm?t=1760529911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/77571eb457a0001debf7f484b17297b5.mp4?t=1760529911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And more thoughts... </h2>Add a Character<br><br>Start adding content to the  wiki on \\fandom<br>Create all the story of the game<br>Make new planets and travelling<br>Add supply pods<br>Manual and Automatic turrets to defend your cities<br>Spaceships to defend your cities<br>Sandbox mode<br>New missions to produce/atack/dominate new places<br>More decorations<br>Mod support using Steam Workshop<br>Sell and buy items in-game (send them to other planets)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/2763923cf4aa5ff9ced01d294bd498e8.poster.avif?t=1760529911\" width=598 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/2763923cf4aa5ff9ced01d294bd498e8.webm?t=1760529911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/2763923cf4aa5ff9ced01d294bd498e8.mp4?t=1760529911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>This is a passion project that will go on for a long time.</strong><br><br>I'm a solo developer who also makes mods for Satisfactory and Factorio.<br><br>Aquila Industrial - Satisfactory Mods<br>DellAquila - Factorio Mods<br><br>Music by JuliusH from Pixabay<br>Italian translation by Micol Pennese<br>Portuguese translation by Andre Aquila<br>German translation by Astradaha<br>French translation by Thierry Lemieux-Raymond<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/7a420f09a086fbdb4675edcdffdcd442.poster.avif?t=1760529911\" width=598 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/7a420f09a086fbdb4675edcdffdcd442.webm?t=1760529911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/7a420f09a086fbdb4675edcdffdcd442.mp4?t=1760529911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/cfda471bba30dc7002c3aad40f60603b.poster.avif?t=1760529911\" width=598 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/cfda471bba30dc7002c3aad40f60603b.webm?t=1760529911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/cfda471bba30dc7002c3aad40f60603b.mp4?t=1760529911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build and protect cities with factories in an infinite hex world.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Best way to play the game: Singleplayer / Mouse and Keyboard.</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Balance production and consumption of your city.<br></li><li> Research new technologies,<br></li><li> Build more factories, <br></li><li> Build more cities,<br></li><li> Explore new tiles and new planets,<br></li><li> Protect your cities from alien sabotage,<br></li><li> Use the Map Maker to build your own worlds, <br></li><li> Get Steam Achievements, <br></li><li> Compare with other players with the Steam Leaderboards!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer Online Stock Exchange.</h2>Reach tier 5 to be able to trade items in the Stock Market with other players online in real-time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/b2d4ed1c7f75b20d0c7a9e948a8fbcb6.poster.avif?t=1760529911\" width=598 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/b2d4ed1c7f75b20d0c7a9e948a8fbcb6.webm?t=1760529911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1958750/extras/b2d4ed1c7f75b20d0c